      "content": "\"Stopping the static\" doesn't mean giving up on life; it means giving up on the *fight* against how things are. It means finding a quiet place inside yourself where the noise can't reach, a place where you don't have to perform or pretend. If stillness feels peaceful, maybe that stillness is what you deserve, and that quiet can be found in a way that doesn't involve the constant, draining struggle.",
